{
  "stem": "15393.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Of course, I didn't understand, at the age of five, what have these people have done?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Suddenly, they were walking, and the police beating them with truncheons.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it was difficult for my parents to explain to me, that they haven't done anything, nothing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were just walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it was a good opportunity to beat up a few Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's how it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was sort of representative of the Polish life, do you think, at the time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very much representative of a [SIGHS] I never like to-- to, and I never will say, of the-- of the Polish nation, of-- it's not.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's-- but of a-- of a certain segment, certainly, certainly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At the universities or if you-- if a student was seen with a Jewish girl, it was a good opportunity to beat him up, even if he wasn't Jewish.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, these things happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But to me, this was sort of [SIGHS] a very--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember that they could not tell me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I couldn't comprehend.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, if they haven't done anything, why are they being beaten and so savagely, you know, with-- with-- with the truncheons?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was a terrible sight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it was the first sight of its kind that I can remember.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that stuck in my memory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were very assimilated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know very much about Jewish life, per se.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I mean I knew I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew my parents wanted to go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we were Jewish, they wanted to build a Jewish state.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All that, I knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I knew that we were going for Passover to my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there, you see, it was quite a different matter, because they were very orthodox.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My mother came through a very, very orthodox background.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
